{"tid":2000123,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港鐵：831兩站閉路電視受破壞　片段不涉後期處理","createTime":"2020-05-03T15:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T13:57:11.000Z","uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fb444e3b5567727107f51c68b8cb1b54e749361f","tid":2000123,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:40:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=389739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D389739&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=281efa14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D389739&h=9a510dcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=389739</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】教育大學學生會前會長梁耀霆早前獲高等法院頒令，要求港鐵提供去年8月31日太子站及荔枝角站的閉路電視片段，但他指片段不齊全，多次要求港鐵提供，但被對方推搪，已於上周三發律師信要求檢視母帶及交代原因。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵回應指已收到有關律師信，正與對方溝通以作安排，重申已於限期內將所有片段交予對方，又指當晚車站受破壞包括閉路電視，其錄影功能亦受損，但所有片段有顯示實時錄影時間，亦不涉及任何後期處理。"},{"pid":"12579670f22d95ba8f1a9ca49ef32a1e6a549dc9","tid":2000123,"uid":58852,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:42:29.000Z","msg":"就算閉路電視俾人破壞，都會認住直到俾人整爛果一刻<br />\n佢究竟知唔知自己講緊啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e521bb3b3f2b8dbcc2363a9fe31fa8f86431f1f","tid":2000123,"uid":253978,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"831之前都無人搞黨鐵<br />\n又屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9663aee22d331d4d1b26ffe9500e1e8d8e776641","tid":2000123,"uid":50502,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"中共:六四沒死人"},{"pid":"771f131663a889ff0154a8ac3b8fda7a7fea1863","tid":2000123,"uid":65790,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:44:57.000Z","msg":"唔齊全喎黨鐵<br />\n咪扮啦<br />\n<br />\n好耐冇裝修？"},{"pid":"6d2dbb3e0a33a653b436e9d2712